description._content: Description: Road on drainage Bank round the Freshwater Lake. Eucalytus tereticornis 4 years old. Elevation 4 feet above sea level. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: Drainage Banks 20 feet wide planted with Eucalyptus - Eucalyptus tereticonis and Stone Pine - Pinus pinea, Age 4 years old, Elevation 3 feet above sea level. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
